      <!-- ══════════════ STAGE 1: 5th–6th ══════════════ -->
      <div class="stage-panel active" id="s5">
        <div class="stage-header fade-in">
          <div class="stage-emoji">🌱</div>
          <div>
            <h2 id="s5-title">Stage 1 — 5th & 6th Standard: Finding Your Voice</h2>
            <p id="s5-desc">At this age, communication is all about being comfortable speaking. You do not need big words — you need confidence to say what you think. Simple, clear, and friendly is the goal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-grid">
          <!-- LISTENING -->
          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">👂</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Listening Skills" data-mr="ऐकण्याचे कौशल्य">Listening Skills</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="The most important skill" data-mr="सर्वात महत्त्वाचे कौशल्य">The most important skill</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Good communication starts with good listening. Most students think speaking is the main skill — but listening is even more important." data-mr="चांगले संवाद चांगल्या ऐकण्यापासून सुरू होतो. बहुतेक विद्यार्थी बोलणे हे मुख्य कौशल्य आहे असे मानतात — पण ऐकणे अधिक महत्त्वाचे आहे.">Good communication starts with good listening. Listening is even more important than speaking.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Look at the person speaking — give them your full attention" data-mr="बोलणाऱ्या व्यक्तीकडे पहा — पूर्ण लक्ष द्या">Look at the person speaking — give full attention</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Do not interrupt — wait for them to finish" data-mr="मध्ये बोलू नका — त्यांना संपू द्या">Do not interrupt — wait for them to finish</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Nod your head to show you are listening" data-mr="ऐकत आहात हे दाखवण्यासाठी मान हलवा">Nod your head to show you are listening</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">4</span><span data-en="Ask one question if something is not clear" data-mr="काही स्पष्ट नसेल तर एक प्रश्न विचारा">Ask one question if something is not clear</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip"><strong data-en="Daily Practice:" data-mr="दैनिक सराव:">Daily Practice:</strong> <span data-en="Listen to a story or news carefully for 5 minutes without doing anything else. Then tell someone 3 things you remember." data-mr="5 मिनिटे काहीही न करता एखादी गोष्ट किंवा बातमी काळजीपूर्वक ऐका. नंतर कोणाला 3 आठवलेल्या गोष्टी सांगा.">Listen to a story for 5 minutes. Then tell someone 3 things you remember.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- SPEAKING CLEARLY -->
          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">🎤</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Speaking Clearly" data-mr="स्पष्ट बोलणे">Speaking Clearly</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="Simple words, said confidently" data-mr="साधे शब्द, आत्मविश्वासाने">Simple words, said confidently</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="You do not need difficult words to speak well. The goal is to speak slowly, clearly, and in complete sentences." data-mr="चांगले बोलण्यासाठी कठीण शब्दांची गरज नाही. उद्दिष्ट आहे हळू, स्पष्ट आणि पूर्ण वाक्यात बोलणे.">You do not need difficult words. Speak slowly, clearly, and in complete sentences.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Think for 3 seconds before you speak" data-mr="बोलण्यापूर्वी 3 सेकंद विचार करा">Think for 3 seconds before you speak</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Speak one idea at a time — do not rush" data-mr="एका वेळी एक कल्पना बोला — घाई करू नका">Speak one idea at a time — don't rush</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Avoid filler words like 'umm', 'aaa', 'matlab'" data-mr="'उम्म', 'आआ', 'मतलब' सारखे भराव शब्द टाळा">Avoid filler words like 'umm', 'aaa'</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">4</span><span data-en="End with a clear conclusion — 'So I think...' or 'My point is...'" data-mr="'म्हणून मला वाटते...' असे स्पष्ट निष्कर्षाने संपवा">End clearly — 'So I think...' or 'My point is...'</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip"><strong data-en="Daily Practice:" data-mr="दैनिक सराव:">Daily Practice:</strong> <span data-en="Every evening, tell someone in your house about your day — in 5 complete sentences. No filler words allowed." data-mr="दर संध्याकाळी घरातील कोणाला तरी तुमच्या दिवसाबद्दल 5 पूर्ण वाक्यांत सांगा. भराव शब्द नाहीत.">Every evening, tell someone about your day in 5 complete sentences.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- READING ALOUD -->
          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">📖</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Reading Aloud" data-mr="मोठ्याने वाचणे">Reading Aloud</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="Pronunciation + confidence together" data-mr="उच्चारण + आत्मविश्वास एकत्र">Pronunciation + confidence together</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Reading aloud is the fastest way to improve your speaking, pronunciation, and confidence — all at the same time." data-mr="मोठ्याने वाचणे हे बोलणे, उच्चारण आणि आत्मविश्वास सुधारण्याचा सर्वात जलद मार्ग आहे — एकाच वेळी.">Reading aloud improves speaking, pronunciation, and confidence — all at the same time.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Read 1 paragraph aloud from your English textbook every day" data-mr="दररोज इंग्रजी पाठ्यपुस्तकातील 1 परिच्छेद मोठ्याने वाचा">Read 1 paragraph from your English book every day</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Read slowly — do not rush through it" data-mr="हळूहळू वाचा — घाई करू नका">Read slowly — never rush through it</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Pay attention to full stops and commas — pause at them" data-mr="पूर्णविराम आणि स्वल्पविरामावर थांबा">Pause at full stops and commas</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">4</span><span data-en="Record yourself on phone — listen back and improve" data-mr="फोनवर स्वतःला रेकॉर्ड करा — ऐका आणि सुधारा">Record yourself on phone — listen back and improve</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip"><strong data-en="Tip:" data-mr="टीप:">Tip:</strong> <span data-en="Start with your Marathi textbook if English feels difficult. Reading aloud in any language builds the speaking habit." data-mr="इंग्रजी कठीण वाटत असेल तर मराठी पाठ्यपुस्तकाने सुरुवात करा. कोणत्याही भाषेत मोठ्याने वाचणे बोलण्याची सवय बनवते.">Start with Marathi textbook if English feels difficult. Any language builds the habit.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ASKING QUESTIONS -->
          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">🙋</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Asking Questions Confidently" data-mr="आत्मविश्वासाने प्रश्न विचारणे">Asking Questions Confidently</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="Smart students always ask" data-mr="हुशार विद्यार्थी नेहमी विचारतात">Smart students always ask</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Many students are afraid to ask questions in class. But asking a question shows you are paying attention — not that you are weak." data-mr="अनेक विद्यार्थी वर्गात प्रश्न विचारण्यास घाबरतात. पण प्रश्न विचारणे तुम्ही लक्ष देत आहात हे दर्शवते — कमकुवतपणा नाही.">Asking questions shows you are paying attention — not that you are weak.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Start with: 'Sir/Ma'am, I want to ask...'" data-mr="'सर/मॅडम, मला विचारायचे आहे...' असे सुरू करा">'Sir/Ma'am, I want to ask...'</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Keep your question short and specific" data-mr="प्रश्न लहान आणि विशिष्ट ठेवा">Keep your question short and specific</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="If you don't understand the answer — it is okay to say 'I still don't understand the second part'" data-mr="'मला दुसरा भाग अजून समजला नाही' असे सांगणे ठीक आहे">'I still don't understand the second part' — it's okay to say this</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip"><strong data-en="Remember:" data-mr="लक्षात ठेवा:">Remember:</strong> <span data-en="Teachers respect students who ask questions. It means you are thinking, not just sitting." data-mr="शिक्षक प्रश्न विचारणाऱ्या विद्यार्थ्यांचा आदर करतात. याचा अर्थ तुम्ही विचार करत आहात, फक्त बसलेले नाही.">Teachers respect students who ask questions. It means you are thinking.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- WEEKLY PRACTICE -->
        <div class="activity-section fade-in">
          <div class="section-heading">📅 <span data-en="Weekly Communication Practice — 5th & 6th Std" data-mr="साप्ताहिक संवाद सराव — ५वी आणि ६वी">Weekly Communication Practice</span></div>
          <div class="week-grid">
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Monday" data-mr="सोमवार">Monday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Read 1 paragraph aloud from English book" data-mr="इंग्रजी पुस्तकातून 1 परिच्छेद मोठ्याने वाचा">Read 1 paragraph aloud from English book</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Tuesday" data-mr="मंगळवार">Tuesday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Tell a family member about your school day — 5 sentences" data-mr="कुटुंबातील सदस्याला तुमच्या शाळेच्या दिवसाबद्दल 5 वाक्यांत सांगा">Tell family about your school day — 5 sentences</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Wednesday" data-mr="बुधवार">Wednesday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Ask 1 question in class today — any subject" data-mr="आज वर्गात 1 प्रश्न विचारा — कोणताही विषय">Ask 1 question in class today</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Thursday" data-mr="गुरुवार">Thursday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Introduce yourself to someone new — name, class, interests" data-mr="एखाद्या नवीन व्यक्तीशी स्वतःची ओळख करून द्या">Introduce yourself to someone new</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Friday" data-mr="शुक्रवार">Friday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Record yourself speaking 2 minutes on 'My favourite subject'" data-mr="'माझा आवडता विषय' वर 2 मिनिटे बोलताना रेकॉर्ड करा">Record yourself for 2 minutes — favourite subject</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Saturday" data-mr="शनिवार">Saturday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Listen to a story or YouTube video — tell 3 points to someone" data-mr="एखादी गोष्ट ऐका — कोणाला 3 मुद्दे सांगा">Listen to a story — tell 3 points to someone</div></div>
            <div class="day-card"><div class="day-name" data-en="Sunday" data-mr="रविवार">Sunday</div><div class="day-task" data-en="Review the week — which day was best? What to improve?" data-mr="आठवडा आढावा — कोणता दिवस सर्वोत्तम होता? काय सुधारायचे?">Review the week — what went best?</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /s5 -->

      <!-- ══════════════ STAGE 2: 7th–8th ══════════════ -->
      <div class="stage-panel" id="s7">
        <div class="stage-header fade-in">
          <div class="stage-emoji">🌿</div>
          <div>
            <h2 id="s7-title">Stage 2 — 7th & 8th Standard: Building Expression</h2>
            <p id="s7-desc">Now you start learning to express opinions, argue points, and participate in group discussions. Your vocabulary grows and your sentences become more confident.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-grid">
          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">💬</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Expressing Opinions" data-mr="मत व्यक्त करणे">Expressing Opinions</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="Say what you think — clearly" data-mr="तुम्हाला काय वाटते ते स्पष्टपणे सांगा">Say what you think — clearly</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Opinion-expressing is a skill. There is a formula to it. Use these phrases to start your opinion." data-mr="मत व्यक्त करणे एक कौशल्य आहे. यासाठी एक सूत्र आहे. मत सुरू करण्यासाठी हे वाक्प्रचार वापरा.">Opinion-expressing has a formula. Use these phrases to start your opinion confidently.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">✓</span><span data-en='"In my opinion..." — use this to start gently' data-mr='"माझ्या मते..." — हळुवारपणे सुरुवात करण्यासाठी वापरा'>"In my opinion..." — gentle way to start</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">✓</span><span data-en='"I think... because..." — give a reason always' data-mr='"मला वाटते... कारण..." — नेहमी कारण द्या'>"I think... because..." — always give a reason</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">✓</span><span data-en='"I agree/disagree with you because..." — polite argument' data-mr='"मी सहमत/असहमत आहे कारण..." — विनम्र वाद'>"I agree / disagree because..." — polite argument</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">✓</span><span data-en='"One example of this is..." — support with example' data-mr='"याचे एक उदाहरण आहे..." — उदाहरणाने समर्थन करा'>"One example of this is..." — support your point</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip" data-en="<strong>Practice:</strong> Pick any topic (e.g. 'Mobile phones should not be allowed in school'). Speak 1 minute FOR it and 1 minute AGAINST it." data-mr="<strong>सराव:</strong> कोणताही विषय निवडा. 1 मिनिट त्याच्या बाजूने आणि 1 मिनिट विरोधात बोला."><strong>Practice:</strong> Pick any topic. Speak 1 min FOR it, 1 min AGAINST it.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">👥</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Group Discussion Skills" data-mr="गट चर्चा कौशल्ये">Group Discussion Skills</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="How to speak when others are also speaking" data-mr="इतर बोलत असताना कसे बोलावे">How to participate when others speak</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Group discussions happen in school projects, class activities, and later in job interviews. Learning them early is very useful." data-mr="गट चर्चा शाळेच्या प्रकल्पांमध्ये, वर्ग उपक्रमांमध्ये आणि नंतर नोकरी मुलाखतींमध्ये होते.">Group discussions happen in school projects and later in job interviews. Learn them early.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Enter the discussion with a point — 'I'd like to add...'" data-mr="एक मुद्दा घेऊन चर्चेत प्रवेश करा — 'मला जोडायचे आहे...'">'I'd like to add...' — enter discussion with a point</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Do not dominate — let everyone speak" data-mr="वर्चस्व गाजवू नका — सर्वांना बोलू द्या">Don't dominate — let everyone speak</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Summarize at the end — 'So we all agree that...'" data-mr="शेवटी सारांश द्या — 'तर आपण सर्वजण सहमत आहोत की...'">'So we all agree that...' — summarize at end</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">4</span><span data-en="Disagree respectfully — never say 'You are wrong'" data-mr="आदराने असहमत व्हा — 'तुम्ही चुकीचे आहात' असे कधीही म्हणू नका">Disagree respectfully — never say 'You are wrong'</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="skill-tip" data-en="<strong>Tip:</strong> In a group discussion, quality matters more than quantity. 2 strong points are better than 10 weak ones." data-mr="<strong>टीप:</strong> गट चर्चेत गुणवत्ता प्रमाणापेक्षा अधिक महत्त्वाची असते. 10 कमकुवत मुद्द्यांपेक्षा 2 मजबूत मुद्दे चांगले."><strong>Tip:</strong> 2 strong points are better than 10 weak ones.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-card fade-in">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <div class="skill-icon">✍️</div>
              <div>
                <div class="skill-title" data-en="Written Communication" data-mr="लिखित संवाद">Written Communication</div>
                <div class="skill-subtitle" data-en="Emails, letters and short notes" data-mr="ईमेल, पत्रे आणि छोट्या नोट्स">Emails, letters and short notes</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="Writing is also communication. In 7th and 8th standard, you learn formal and informal letter writing. This directly helps in board exams later." data-mr="लेखन देखील संवाद आहे. 7वी आणि 8वीत तुम्ही औपचारिक आणि अनौपचारिक पत्र लेखन शिकता.">Writing is communication too. Formal and informal letter writing directly helps in board exams.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Formal letters — always use 'Respected Sir/Ma'am'" data-mr="औपचारिक पत्रे — नेहमी 'आदरणीय सर/मॅडम' वापरा">Formal: 'Respected Sir/Ma'am'</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="State your purpose in the first line clearly" data-mr="पहिल्याच ओळीत उद्देश स्पष्टपणे सांगा">State your purpose in the first line</span></li>
