              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="Prepare your 3 main points — not a full script" data-mr="तुमचे 3 मुख्य मुद्दे तयार करा — पूर्ण स्क्रिप्ट नाही">Prepare 3 main points — not a full script</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Start with a question or surprising fact — grab attention" data-mr="प्रश्न किंवा आश्चर्यकारक तथ्याने सुरुवात करा — लक्ष खेचा">Start with a question or surprising fact</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Speak to the back of the room — everyone will hear you" data-mr="खोलीच्या मागच्या भागाकडे बोला — सर्वांना ऐकू येईल">Speak to the back of the room — everyone hears you</span></li>
