            <div class="skill-body">
              <p class="skill-desc" data-en="A debate is not a fight. It is a structured way to present and defend your point. Schools hold inter-school debates — and students who learn this early have an advantage." data-mr="वाद हा भांडण नाही. हे तुमचा मुद्दा सादर करण्याचा आणि बचाव करण्याचा संरचित मार्ग आहे.">A debate is structured argument — not a fight. Learn it early for big advantages.</p>
              <ul class="steps-list">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span data-en="State your position clearly in the first 2 sentences" data-mr="पहिल्या 2 वाक्यांत तुमची स्थिती स्पष्टपणे सांगा">State your position clearly in first 2 sentences</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span data-en="Give 2–3 strong reasons with examples" data-mr="उदाहरणांसह 2–3 मजबूत कारणे द्या">Give 2–3 reasons with examples</span></li>
