                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span data-en="Sit straight, make eye contact, and speak at medium pace" data-mr="सरळ बसा, डोळ्यांशी संपर्क ठेवा आणि मध्यम गतीने बोला">Sit straight, eye contact, medium pace</span></li>
