          <div class="section-desc" data-en="A realistic 12-month preparation roadmap for a current 12th student targeting 150+ in JEE Main." data-mr="JEE Main मध्ये 150+ टार्गेट करणाऱ्या सध्याच्या 12वी विद्यार्थ्यासाठी 12 महिन्यांचा वास्तवादी तयारी रोडमॅप.">A realistic 12-month roadmap for a 12th student targeting 150+ in JEE Main. Adjust targets based on your current level.</div>

          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="tl-step">
              <div class="tl-left"><div class="tl-circle">Jun–Aug</div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-badge badge-blue">Phase 1: Foundation (June–Aug 2025)</div>
                <h4>Complete 11th Syllabus + Start 12th Early</h4>
                <p>Revise all 11th Physics, Chemistry, Math (50% of JEE). Solve NCERT examples. Maintain formula notebooks. Start Chapters: Electrostatics (Phy), Organic Chemistry (Chem), Calculus (Math). Daily: 4–5 hrs study + school.</p>
