              <div class="tl-left"><div class="tl-circle">Sep–Oct</div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-badge badge-gold">Phase 2: 12th New Topics (Sep–Oct 2025)</div>
                <h4>Complete Current Electricity, Organics, Integration</h4>
                <p>All new 12th chapters. Solve coaching material + NCERT. Start solving previous year JEE Mains (2019–2024) chapter-wise. First attempt at mock tests — identify weak areas. Join test series if not already in coaching.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-step">
              <div class="tl-left"><div class="tl-circle">Nov–Dec</div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
