                <h4>Finish All Chapters + Start Full Mocks</h4>
                <p>All topics covered by December 15. Start full-length JEE Mock Tests every Sunday. Score 80+ in mocks. Fix one "strong chapter" per subject. Prelim boards practical exams — don't ignore.</p>
