              <div class="tl-left"><div class="tl-circle">Jan</div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
              <div class="tl-content">
                <div class="tl-badge badge-green">JEE MAIN SESSION 1 — January 2026</div>
                <h4>Give Your Best! Session 1 attempt</h4>
                <p>Don't study new topics in last 7 days — only revision. Sleep 7 hrs before exam. Attempt Maths first (most time-consuming), then Chemistry (fastest), then Physics. Mark all numericals — no negative. Target 120–160 minimum.</p>
